EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN COALESCE(PARTY_EFFEC_DATE,'') <> '' AND PARTY_EFFEC_DATE <> '2069-12-31'  THEN to_date(TRIM(PARTY_EFFEC_DATE), 'yyyy-MM-dd') WHEN PARTY_EFFEC_DATE = '2069-12-31' THEN to_date('9999-12-31', 'yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-dd') END
